title: True North
description: Over 1,000 mods, combining 14+ years of the Skyrim modding communitys work into one cohesive, optimized experience. Fully voiced main character (can turn off), survival gameplay (can turn off), experience Skyrim transform as winter arrives, draping every hold in a stunning blanket of snow. Combat has been rebuilt from the ground up with modern animations (BFCO) and AI. Every notable questline has been expanded to provide more role playing opportunitys. Hours of new content. Highly immersive and reactive ever-evolving world that never drops below 60 FPS
author: Truman
